text.tspan: Based on the assessments and index by Polity 5 (2021), weighted by countries' populations. It captures the extent to which open, multi-party,
and competitive elections choose a chief executive who faces comprehensive institutional constraints, and political participation is
competitive. It ranges from -10 to 10 (fully democratic).
